      • generateSendableData

        KeySendableData generateSendableData()
        This function is used when an El Gamal Private Key needs to be sent via a Channel or any other means of sending data (including serialization). It retrieves all the data needed to reconstruct this Private Key at a later time and/or in a different VM. It puts all the data in an instance of the relevant class that implements the KeySendableData interface.
        Returns:
        the KeySendableData object
